        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Everybody used to talk about the go-go 80's like they were so wonderful. Well, the 80's were like child's play. It is ridiculous now. The amount of time and stress that my people have had to put up with is inhuman.''</p>
        <p>JOHN TORTORELLA, who builds swimming pools in the Hamptons. [B4]</p>
      </block>
